    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that makes me feel way better a bit nervous about it. actually i'm also taking some leftover antibiotics from a different infection i had last month, do you think i should take those too just to be safe and make sure the infection at the surgery site really clears out? i have plenty left over so i could just take a few days worth.",
